{"tid":2218814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動資訊戰] Report大量牛鬼蛇神五毛垃圾youtube！(附教學)(2)","createTime":"2020-09-26T13:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T01:55:35.000Z","uid":226829,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88b5831b205b6cb605eea4b42c3b2ef61abea6ea","tid":2218814,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"有痴線佬整理左大量牛鬼蛇神三毛垃圾channel，趁而家瀨共google  youtube終於(逼著)正常，剷左2500支頻，打鐵趁熱，大家一齊report！<br />\n<br />\n要<span class=\"red\">全個channel report，<strong><span class=\"x-large\">必須用電腦網頁版</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n注意，喺牛鬼蛇神五毛垃圾channel頁面，建議避免以下教學以外既操作，以免誤加view數、或令youtube運算誤會你既取向，向你推介同類垃圾片，令你不安反感。<br />\n<br />\n首先撳link(在樓下)，到「關於」(ABOUT)頁面(如無意外link已直達)，撳「統計資料」(Stats)下既旗仔，不用「封鎖」，揀「檢舉使用者」(Report user)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YeoOis7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYeoOis7.jpg&h=bb9d7dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀「垃圾內容和詐騙」(Spam and scams)、「繼續」(NEXT)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9RgsqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9RgsqW.jpg&h=7a10a215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可揀可唔揀，隨便揀幾條就手既就得、「繼續」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzWPNrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzWPNrp.jpg&h=2999c98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n填以下內容，或自由發揮<br />\n<br />\n激進版： This sole purpose of the channel is to spread Chinese Communist Party propaganda and fake news, and has blatantly advocated for the suppression of freedom and human rights in Hong Kong. This kind of political propaganda has no place on YouTube.<br />\n<br />\n溫和左膠版： This channel has been spreading propaganda for the Chinese Communist Party. They're part of the smear campaign of the CCP, targeting the freedom-loving people in the US, Hong Kong, Taiwan and Tibet, and to interfere with the 2020 US election.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Y8FT6t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Y8FT6t.jpg&h=fcacf463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「提交」(SUBMIT)，攪掂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，手足貼呢類link的話，最好貼直入「關於」頁既link，方法是先撳去「關於」頁，再copy條link(見條link最尾係about就是了)，咁樣手足一入就到「關於」頁，避免首面可能自動播片而增加view數，同時「關於」頁有得撳旗仔，方便report。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如不要貼<br />\n<del><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/leetszking/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fleetszking%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=cb8bc2a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/leetszking/</a></del><br />\n<br />\n試著貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/leetszking/about\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fleetszking%2Fabout&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=bfba23c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/leetszking/about</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">最後來個認真mode</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家明白，呢家係戰爭狀態，對手係全球最大黑社會。<br />\n要贏呢場戰爭，要成功光復香港，資訊戰並係其中一個好重要既戰線。<br />\n<br />\n請大家打醒十二分精神，打好呢場資訊戰。<br />\n這是一場硬仗，不容鬆懈。一但任由其對家勢力壯大，煲底之約定必遙遙無期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港</span></strong></span>[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=3]大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-aut